[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "カウントダウンフェス。\n年越しに合わせて行われるカウントダウンライブの１つ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00432",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "様々なジャンルのアーティストやアイドルグループが\n一堂に会するビッグイベント",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00433",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "皆さん知っていますわよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00434",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "知ってるに決まってるよ！　年末にテレビで\n見るものといったらそれしかないくらいだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00435",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "まさかそれに出演できるってわけ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00436",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そんなはずがありません。主催者からオファーを\n受けたアーティストのみが出演できるはず",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00437",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そうですわね。基本的には",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00438",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……そう言うってことは、何か手があるのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00439",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "「公募枠」というものがありますわ。\n審査を受け、勝ち残った者が出演権を獲得できますの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00440",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "とはいえ、その枠はごくごく少数……\nわたくしたちはその枠を勝ち取らなくてはなりません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00441",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "審査とは、何を評価されるのですか？\nやはり、歌やダンスの技量でしょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00442",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "一言で表すのであれば……「人気」ですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00443",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ライブの動員実績、ＳＮＳのフォロワー数、\nそして直近の勢い、エトセトラ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00444",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そういったものを総合的に見て\n判定されているようですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00445",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はあ！？　それ、私たちに勝ち目あるわけ？\nこの前デビューしたばかりで、ファンも少ないのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00446",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "審査開始までに１週間ありますわ。そこまでに、\n全力で「人気」を獲得すれば良いだけのこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00447",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そんなの、簡単にいくわけ――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00448",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "言い訳を並べるのは結構。\n……ですが、せっかくのチャンスを棒に振るのですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00449",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……っ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00450",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "生存競争の激しい世界ですわ。少しずつ、一歩一歩。\nそんなことを言っていたら置いていかれてしまうのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00451",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "世界一のアイドルになる。そう仰っていましたが、\nあなたにはそのための計画がありますの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00452",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00453",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "前に言っていた、わたくしの計画。\nそれはこのフェスを目指したものでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00454",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "だからこそ急いでライブを重ね、\n実績を作る必要がありましたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00455",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ま、まあ？　たとえ選ばれなかったとしても、\n人気になることはいいことだと思うし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00456",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "とにかくやってみようよ！\n面白そうだしね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00457",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そうでございまするな。そのサポートは\n期待して良いのでしょう？　社長殿",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00458",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "もちろん。ですがまずはあなたがたが現状を自覚し、\n自ら動くことが大切ですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00459",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "わたくしは、皆さんがアイドルとして大成するための\n最短ルートを切り拓いて差し上げます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00460",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そこから先は、皆さんの努力次第。\n必要以上の支援は期待しないこと。いいですわね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00461",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……分かったわ。やるわよ。\nやってみせようじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00462",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "見てなさいよ！　ぎゃふんと言わせてやるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00463",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。楽しみにしていますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00464",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]